rerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="山姆·芬德（Sam Fender） - 电视晚餐（直播首次亮相）-Paris 4K UHD" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/K7UfxIfU5Ns?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h2><strong>山姆·芬德（Sam Fender）的巴黎集体清单是：</strong></h2><p> <strong>1。“入门”</strong><br /> <strong>2。“手臂的长度”</strong><br /> <strong>3。“人们看着”</strong><br /> <strong>4。“崩溃帝国”（现场处女作）</strong><br /> <strong>5。“我们会说话吗？”</strong><br /> <strong>6。“暴君”（现场处女作）</strong><br /> <strong>7。&#39;Howdon Aldi死亡队列&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>8。“电视晚餐”（直播首次亮相）</strong><br /> <strong>9。“吐你”</strong><br /> <strong>10。“寄宿生”</strong><br /> <strong>11。“一点近一点”</strong><br /> <strong>12。“十七岁</strong><br /><strong>13。“下巴”（现场处女作）</strong><br /> <strong>14。“超声导弹”</strong></p><p>这次巡回演出将于今晚（3月5日）在蒂尔堡的013 Poppodium场地举行，随后在整个月举行苏黎世，科隆，慕尼黑，柏林，阿姆斯特丹等等。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.com/sam-fender-tickets/artist/2417706?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=w5HRQ%3A3B9xyPUUd0HkSfkSRTUksw8Oyo2VNEVg0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处</a>剩下的门票。</p><p>至于“人们观看的人”，这张专辑上个月到达，并在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/harry-styles">哈利·斯泰尔斯（Harry Styles）</a> “<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/harry-styles-new-album-harrys-house-3226209">哈利的家”（Harry&#39;s House</a> ） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fenders-people-watching-earns-biggest-uk-opening-week-for-british-act-since-harry-styles-harrys-house-3842384">开始了英国最大的开幕周</a>。它还标志着Fender有史以来最大的开幕周，售出的单位超过2019年的首次亮相“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/sam-fender-hypersonic-missiles-review-2546624">Hypersonic导弹</a>”和2021年的“<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sam-fender-seventeen-going-under-review-3060680">十七岁</a>”。</p><p> <em>NME</em>在对“观看者”的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sam-fender-people-watching-review-3840019">四星级评论</a>中写道：“反思性，分析性和脆弱性，“观看的人”确实做了标题可能所暗示的：盘点使Fender成为他今天的人的角色，朋友和亲人。当他回顾迄今为止的生活时，他以敏感的方式接近每条曲目，甚至有罪恶感，也要考虑下一个可能是谁。”</p><p>在其他山姆·芬德（Sam Fender）新闻中，这位音乐家最近嘲笑了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-continues-to-tease-another-new-album-says-hes-desperate-to-make-a-punk-album-3840765">另一张新专辑，他说他“拼命”倾向于朋克风格的声音</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sam-fender-perform-and-give-shout-out-to-newcastle-and-north-shields-at-the-brit-awards-2025-3842681">利用他的英国人演讲来庆祝纽卡斯尔人民。</a></p><p>帖子观看山姆·芬德（Sam Fender）在欧洲巡回演唱会上首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sam-fender-people-watching-songs-live-debut-european-tour-setlist-gootage-3843710">上时，让“人们观看”歌曲的现场亮相</a>。</p> ;
肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）的照片表面有可能获得大学学位https://www.nme.com/news/music/photos-surface-of-kendrick-lamar-potential-potenty--a-a-college-degree-3842407?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = kendrick-lamar-potiently-potientally-a-college-a-college-a-college-a-college-a-college-a-college-a-college-a-college-a-college学位Kyann-Sian WilliamsWed, 05 Mar 2025 09:53:31 +0000 Music NewsNewsHip-hopRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3842407 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-2000x1270-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）。图片来源：Kevin Mazur/Getty Images" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-2000x1270-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-2000x1270-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-2000x1270-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-2000x1270-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-2000x1270-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-2000x1270-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>加州大学洛杉矶分校（UCLA）确认拉马尔（Lamar）已注册，吹嘘：“加州大学洛杉矶分校是您的升级的地方”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/photos-surface-of-kendrick-lamar-potentially-earning-a-college-degree-3842407">肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）的邮政照片表面潜在获得大学学位，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-2000x1270-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）。图片来源：Kevin Mazur/Getty Images" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-2000x1270-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-2000x1270-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-2000x1270-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-2000x1270-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-2000x1270-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-2000x1270-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据称的<a href="/artists/kendrick-lamar">肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）</a>的同学在2022年的演讲中分享了他的照片，称说唱歌手是“令人难以置信的善良和谦虚”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/how-kendrick-lamar-and-drakes-beef-has-impacted-their-ticket-sales-3837764">肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）和德雷克（Drake）的牛肉如何影响他们的门票销售</a></strong></li></ul><p>在世界上不为人知的是，拉马尔（Lamar）于2022年在加州大学洛杉矶分校（UCLA）参加了心理学课程。上周三（2月26日），同学同学拍摄的照片被网上发布，显示了康普顿明星专心写下笔记，并在讲座厅里自己在桌子上使用他的电话。</p><p>同学们还评论说（根据Instagram粉<a href="https://www.instagram.com/kendricklamarzz/?utm_source=ig_embed" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>丝肯德里克拉兹（Kendricklicklamazz</em></a> ））：“他非常友善和谦虚。我当时没有意识到他是谁 - 我只是看到人们要照片，我也拍了一些照片。直到后来有人告诉我他是谁。”</p><p>加州大学洛杉矶分校还证实，拉马尔已经在大学入学并上了课，发推文说：“ 2022年的照片，但课程保持不变 -  UCLA是您升级的地方<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f4da.png" alt="📚" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/270d.png" alt="✍" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> 。”在此处查看帖子： </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGjTLP6pCoH/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 