><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mumford-sons-announce-tiny-free-show-in-london-tonight-3843486">Mumford＆Sons</a>昨晚在伦敦演出了一对即兴的弹出声演出 - 请参阅下面的镜头。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mumford-sons-announce-tiny-free-show-in-london-tonight-3843486">昨天早上宣布</a>昨晚（3月4日）在伦敦市中心的420个容量扁铁广场上演出。由于场地以外的队列的长度，他们决定弹奏第二盘，以使尽可能多的人参加。</p><p>这两种唱片都由六首歌曲组成，三人在站在长桌子上，被推到临时阶段。除了诸如“小狮子人”和“我会等待”之类的招牌歌曲之外，他们在两种表演中都播放了新曲目“ Caroline”和“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mumford-sons-share-rousing-comeback-single-and-title-track-from-forthcoming-new-album-rushmere-3829824">Rushmere</a> ”。</p><p>请参阅此处的亲密节目的粉丝捕获镜头： </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DGyx-R1CTm5/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.