="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预享用</a>）发行他们的第五张录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mumford-sons-share-rousing-comeback-single-and-title-track-from-forthcoming-new-album-rushmere-3829824">“ Rushmere”</a> 。在2018年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/mumford-sons-delta-review-2402736">“ Delta”</a>之后的唱片已经通过<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mumford-sons-share-rousing-comeback-single-and-title-track-from-forthcoming-new-album-rushmere-3829824">标题曲目</a>和单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mumford-sons-share-new-rushmere-album-opener-malibu-this-song-just-felt-like-us-3839133">“ Malibu”</a>预览。</p><p> “ Rushmere”标记了Mumford＆Sons&#39;的第一个LP，包括Mumford，Ted Dwane和Ben Lovett。温斯顿·马歇尔（Winston Marshall）在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mumford-sons-winston-marshall-praises-brave-right-wing-agitator-andy-ngo-2895342">面对右翼美国记者安迪·非政府组织（Andy Ngo）的一本书</a>之后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mumford-sons-winston-marshall-quits-band-after-praising-right-wing-agitator-andy-ngo-2977520">于2021年离开了该小组</a>。</p><p>该唱片是由Mumford＆Sons的“传奇朋友” Dave Cobb共同制作的，他曾与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brandi-carlile">Brandi Carlile</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-stapleton">Chris Stapleton</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slash">Slash</a>等人合作。</p><p>乐队还将在今年春季演奏一系列英国唱片商店的日期，包括在伦敦的Rough Trade East露面。<a href="https://www.mumfordandsons.com/tour/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里找到完整的行程</a>。</p><p> 《邮<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-mumford-sons-play-two-acoustic-pop-up-shows-in-london-3843703">报》在伦敦播放了两个声学弹出式节目，该邮报</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现在伦敦。</p> ;
