ackground-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 20px; width: 20px;"></div><div style=" width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 2px solid transparent; border-left: 6px solid #f4f4f4; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; transform: translateX(16px) translateY(-4px) rotate(30deg)"></div></div><div style="margin-left: auto;"><div style=" width: 0px; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-right: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(16px);"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; flex-grow: 0; height: 12px; width: 16px; transform: translateY(-4px);"></div><div style=" width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-left: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(-4px) translateX(8px);"></div></div></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 24px;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 224px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 144px;"></div></div><p></p><p style=" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:17px; margin-bottom:0; margin-top:8px; overflow:hidden; padding:8px 0 7px; text-align:center; text-overflow:ellipsis; white-space:nowrap;"> <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGtPlqAIXPk/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" style=" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px; text-decoration:none;" target="_blank">Shade Borough（@theshadeborough）共享的帖子</a></p></div></blockquote><p><script async src="//platform.instagram.com/en_US/embeds.js"></script></p><p>西北伦敦说唱传奇人物Bashy于去年7月发行了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bashy-on-being-poor-is-expensive-first-album-in-15-years-ididnt-know-whether-i-was-gonna-make-3773615-3773615">他备受赞誉的第二张专辑《贫穷的IS昂贵》</a> - 他在2009年的首次亮相“如果可以的话”之后，他在15年内发行了第一张全长发行。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/here-are-all-the-winners-from-the-mobo-awards-2025-3839156">该唱片赢得了说唱歌手Two Mobos for Best Hip Hop Act和年度专辑</a>。</p><p> Grime Icon Ghetts于2024年2月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ghetts-announces-new-album-on-purpose-with-purpose-conflict-of-interest-3515809">放弃了他的第四张录音室专辑“有目的的目的”</a> ，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mercury-prize-2024-check-out-the-shortlisted-nominees-here-3777869">入围了去年的Mercury Prive</a> 。在四星级的评论中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/ghetts-on-purpose-with-purpose-review-lyrics-tracklist-3591858"><em>NME</em>称赞该唱片</a>“不仅仅是一张写得很好，具有社会意识的说唱专辑”。取而代之的是，这是“如何制作成长的说唱音乐而不弄脏数十年来建造的遗产的完美展示”。</p><p>两者“穷人都是昂贵的”和“有目的的目的”都在<a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-albums-2024-3818995"><em>NME</em>的2024年列表中的最佳专辑中分别在31和21中排名</a>。</p><p>一月份，Cench丢下了<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/central-cee-cant-rush-greatness-review-radar-3831625">“ Credy Greatness”， <em>NME</em>给了四颗星星</a>：“ Central Cee可以很容易地隐藏在他标志性的神秘之后，而是讲述了一个男孩在世界舞台上都变成男人的故事。没有烟雾和镜子，专辑实际上是在每一步的每一步。”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/here-are-all-the-winners-from-the-mobo-awards-2025-3839156">Central Cee在今年的Mobos中获得了第三次创纪录的男性表演</a>。这是他在仪式上的第七场胜利，用Stormzy将他绑在一起，并使他们俩都是历史上装饰最多的说唱歌手。</p><p>他将在4月1日在欧洲的Spektrum开始欧洲<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fcentral-cee-tickets%2Fartist%2F5347483" target="_blank" rel="noopener">的世界巡回演唱</a>会来参加专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/central-cee-announces-cant-rush-greatness-2025-world-tour-3832644">。在这里查看一份完整的约会列表</a>，并在此处访问这里购买英国门票， <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fcentral-cee-tickets%2Fartist%2F2774375" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买美国门票，并<a href="https://us.centralcee.com/pages/live" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买澳大利亚门票。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/central-cee-confirmed-as-final-headliner-for-boardmasters-2025-3833282">Cench还将</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">Raye</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-prodigy">The Prodigy</a>一起在今年八月的董事会音乐节上头条新闻。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/central-cee-manager-comments-on-stormzys-brit-speech-i-dont-necessarily-think-cench-deserved-to-win-3843066">Central Cee的经理在Stormzy&#39;s Brits演讲中：“我不一定认为Cench应该赢得胜利”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
