3039">美国梦</a>”的后续活动。新单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-lcd-soundsystems-surprise-new-single-x-ray-eyes-3805182">“ X射线眼”</a>于去年11月发行，LCD Soundsystem的第五张专辑在今年的某个时候发行。</p><p> LCD Soundsystem以前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-announce-anniversary-residency-at-brixton-academy-3175736">在2022年接管了O2 Academy Brixemy，获得了六晚居留</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/lcd-soundsystem-glastonbury-2024-pyramid-review-setlist-photos-3769986">在格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）取得了胜利的金字塔舞台表演</a>之后，他们还在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-all-points-east-london-uk-tour-line-up-pixies-tickets-3551502">2024年成为所有Point的东部节日</a>。乐队以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-announce-winter-2024-nyc-winter-function-residency-buy-tickets-3795250">著名的纽约“冬季职能”居住</a>结束了这一年，并已经确认了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-announce-2025-us-tour-3831914">本月晚些时候的美国标题巡回演出，</a>并在包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/primavera-sound-2025-line-up-announced-tickets-3805796">巴塞罗那的Primavera Sound（包括巴黎的Primavera Sound）</a>一起，我们喜欢巴黎的Green。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/priority-tickets-lcd-soundsystem-london-residency-onsale-3843499">LCD Soundsystem的伦敦居留权的邮政优先票现已</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
