-content/uploads/2025/03/seventeen-svt-wonwoo-military-mandatory-service-enlist-april-2025-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/seventeen-svt-wonwoo-military-mandatory-service-enlist-april-2025-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/seventeen-svt-wonwoo-military-mandatory-service-enlist-april-2025-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/seventeen-svt-wonwoo-military-mandatory-service-enlist-april-2025-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/seventeen-svt-wonwoo-military-mandatory-service-enlist-april-2025-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他的唱片公司证实，下个月将有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/seventeen">17名</a>成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wonwoo">Wonwoo</a>将于下个月入伍。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/seventeens-bss-teleparty-review-3827041">十七的BSS带来复古的派对曲调，以唱“电信”上的蓝调</a></strong></li></ul><p>今天（3月5日），十七的Wonwoo和他的唱片公司<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/pledis-entertainment">Pledis Entertainment</a>发表了一份声明，声明<a href="https://weverse.io/seventeen/notice/25463">Weverse</a>宣布了K-Pop偶像即将举行的军事入伍。它写道：“我们想分享一个消息，即17岁的Wonwoo将从今年4月3日开始强制性服兵役。”</p><p>结果，这位K-Pop明星将错过在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/seventeen-to-headline-mexicos-tecate-pal-norte-music-festival-in-2025-3807739">墨西哥的Tecate Pa&#39;l Norte音乐节</a>和日本的粉丝界的男生头条新闻，这两者都在入伍后进行。但是，Wonwoo将继续出现在本月晚些时候在首尔举行的即将到来的“ Caratland”粉丝上，并在精选的预录内容中。</p><p> Pledis Entertainment补充说：“在他入伍的那天将没有官方活动，我们请您避免访问他的替代兵役地点。” “我们要求您继续对艺术家的爱和支持，直到他安全健康的回归为止。 We will also stay committed to providing Wonwoo with all the necessary support during this time.”</p><p> Wonwoo will be second member of SEVENTEEN to enlist, following <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/seventeen-jeonghan-to-enlist-in-the-military-later-this-month-3792994">Jeonghan who began his service in September 2024</a> . Other members of the boyband expected to enlist by the end of the year include <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/seventeen-hoshi-woozi-debut-sub-unit-beam-3839222">Hoshi and Woozi, both of whom are currently gearing up to debut as a new sub-unit.</a></p><p> In January, Hoshi also released new music with separate SEVENTEEN sub-unit <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/seventeen-bss-single-album-teleparty-trailer-release-3824912">BSS, completed by Seungkwan and DK, via the single album &#39;Teleparty&#39;</a> . It included title track &#39;CBZ (Prime Time)&#39; and marked the trio&#39;s first comeback since they released &#39;Second Wind&#39; in early 2023.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/seventeen-wonwoo-enlist-military-service-april-3843678">SEVENTEEN&#39;s Wonwoo to enlist for military service in April</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
